snippet.title: Kingdom Hearts HD 2.8 Final Chapter Prologue E3 2016 Trailer
snippet.description:
Kingdom Hearts 2.8 Final Chapter Prologue will be released globally in December 2016! 
 
In this new trailer, experience Aqua’s battle against the Heartless in KINGDOM HEARTS 0.2 Birth by Sleep -A fragmentary passage, new HD gameplay from KH Dream Drop Distance & new scenes from KHχ Back Cover that sheds light on the mysterious Foretellers!

Follow us for more updates on Kingdom Hearts HD 2.8 Final Chapter Prologue:

Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/KingdomHearts
Twitter – https://www.twitter.com/KingdomHearts 
Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/KingdomHearts
